{
  "texts": [
    "They possess creativity, intelligence, and the capacity to adapt their strategies, making them a persistent risk despite the advanced defenses offered by AI.",
    "They can utilize techniques like \"data poisoning\" or \"adversarial attacks\" to manipulate the learning process of AI systems.",
    "AI-POWERED CYBER ATTACKWhen in the hands of a malicious hands, AI can become a potent tool for automating and scaling cyber threats.",
    "With AI, cybercriminals can swiftly adapt to defensive measures, carry out attacks at unprecedented speeds, and exploit vulnerabilities with heightened precision.",
    "AI can even enable attackers to mimic human behavior, making phishing attacks more convincing and likely to succeed."
  ]
}